lEX4QLHL9TlMF9szKYks5gAw14yKM2-MijNs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075380%2Forg%2F6e13141df2197b018490e13060111473.png%2FEyawrNrlEX4QLHL9TlMF9szKYks5gAw14yKM2-MijNs&h=5b43ea82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3075378/org/8ec80d13e434a4c1f0ad7555a8a3a135.png/ie39cHcOL7wZi7v4Rb53EKdIZgoeBhAGFCZbiRQmW4k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075378%2Forg%2F8ec80d13e434a4c1f0ad7555a8a3a135.png%2Fie39cHcOL7wZi7v4Rb53EKdIZgoeBhAGFCZbiRQmW4k&h=1cef13d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e22924c4c2dabd14012cb90ea706ea3af07831d","tid":1370439,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:10:47.000Z","msg":"一直都以三合會為主題的連載漫畫《古惑仔》，由牛佬主編，以及一班漫畫家一起製作。近日，《古惑仔》漫畫在社交平台分享新一期漫畫封面，畫作可見一班身穿白衣的男子舉棍﹑手持鐵通向群眾毆打的畫面，這不難讓大家回想起7月21日晚上在元朗發生的一切。<br />\n<br />\n而除了在漫畫上一直以社會事件作為創作的概念，由漫畫演變出來的電影《古惑仔》電影系列，其實也有不少啜核對白和情節在諷刺時弊，既反映當時社會狀況，甚至具警世的預視作用。<br />\n<br />\n牛佬主編的《古惑仔》一直有諷刺時弊，反映當時香港的各種社會問題。明天（25/7）出版的最新一集漫畫，就以「拯救金尊貴」為題，封面畫上有十多名白衣人士，手持鐵通向部分戴著頭盔、舉起雨傘的市民揮棍。這個場面逼真到不得了，不難讓讀者會聯想起7月21日，當晚在元朗西鐵站發生的市民及港鐵乘客無故被襲擊的事件。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>漫畫都要光復十八區</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實，漫畫《古惑仔》一直都有以香港社會事件等問題去創作，例如：近日都有以「反送中」示威衝突為背景，早前漫畫曾以「出嚟隻揪」等主題，加上配圖，就會讓人想起現實中發生過的事，警民衝突等問題。而在2014 年的雨傘運動時，《古惑仔》都曾以疑似紋身警察諷剌黑警，以主角陳浩南手持黃雨傘的畫作，表示支持當時的公民抗爭。除了封面，內容也有暗喻，因為故事發展到香港被台灣黑社會毒蛇幫入侵，並已潛伏18區。作為洪興的陳浩南當然要行最前，並已行動勢言要光復18區。"},{"pid":"0471c10ecd9540e8d5f365640632e98379632d51","tid":1370439,"uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>牛佬︰「警民衝突場面，百年難得一見」</strong><br />\n<br />\n而漫畫主編牛佬日前都有在網上貼文指，今期封面先主題，頗為特別，指出今期內容是描述近日「警民衝突」的經典場面，又指這情況在香港來說，真的是「百年難得一見」，所以近期的作品都「值得一眾老友記擁有留念」。就着最近的作品，香港01記者曾聯絡牛佬，希望了解更多其創作的想法，但暫時未有收到回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>蔣天養對陳浩南的一番話</strong><br />\n<br />\n而由漫畫《古惑仔》改編的香港電影系列《古惑仔》，由鄭伊健、陳小春、朱永棠、謝天華、林曉峰等人主演，其實不少情節、對白都相當近貼時事，有時候也會在戲中看到很多社會問題。例如在《98古惑仔之龍爭虎鬥》電影中，飾演黑幫大佬蔣天養的萬梓良，就對飾演陳浩南的鄭伊健說過一番話：「香港這地方，97回歸之後雖說是五十年不變，但他們蔣家樹大招風，他們在北京那邊已經盯上我們了。」蔣天養繼續說，「從前行古惑是靠體力，不是智慧。」但時代不同了，他提醒陳浩南「現在行古惑，也要用頭腦，跟京官打交道同樣要用腦。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：劉希彤<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/355784/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E5%8F%A4%E6%83%91%E4%BB%94-%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E7%A5%9E%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%88%E5%B0%8D%E7%99%BD%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E5%A5%BD%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F355784%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%2583%2591%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%258E%259F-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B8%2596&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=4df4f20d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/355784/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E5%8F%A4%E6%83%91%E4%BB%94-%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E7%A5%9E%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%88%E5%B0%8D%E7%99%BD%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E5%A5%BD%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%96</a>"},{"pid":"5f8da127cd5c131f11f402095a8c03540a35892a","tid":1370439,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>漫畫《古惑仔》封面　重現白衣人無差別襲擊市民一幕</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3075391/org/3bbc3bce7d6791724a3dbe8887b1f4f6.jpg/SzBaMczA-MN2rN9c0jkJojVk0lowvFpxUYsK91GLCvc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075391%2Forg%2F3bbc3bce7d6791724a3dbe8887b1f4f6.jpg%2FSzBaMczA-MN2rN9c0jkJojVk0lowvFpxUYsK91GLCvc&h=0c539cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3075393/org/e5cac3f5714b4b927e6257434bcbee1e.jpg/f7kCAhVgGC6d59uAVWbLMd9GeZc8iQN5hLyN2oS8jdo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075393%2Forg%2Fe5cac3f5714b4b927e6257434bcbee1e.jpg%2Ff7kCAhVgGC6d59uAVWbLMd9GeZc8iQN5hLyN2oS8jdo&h=cfd2cf69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3075167/org/aff460af32469f2a1f4cb03b81bab706.jpg/BBPvgwto_iMXFOwaJjOJvUEADLWNycfBocZXuaHGV7k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075167%2Forg%2Faff460af32469f2a1f4cb03b81bab706.jpg%2FBBPvgwto_iMXFOwaJjOJvUEADLWNycfBocZXuaHGV7k&h=9b858951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3075168/org/95d9ba83adcaac5117ffddb426d147f4.jpg/F3njUIHhQsAhKyYJJG3x1_QTmA6yFRx2t0rpsLdK6bA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075168%2Forg%2F95d9ba83adcaac5117ffddb426d147f4.jpg%2FF3njUIHhQsAhKyYJJG3x1_QTmA6yFRx2t0rpsLdK6bA&h=0991504a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3075272/org/aeb0ba791f12ecb43b0b19ecd682de37.jpg/eKi7Y4p3uz_36g6rLaM1zh6RNWq3NHf-hqtZy4arWcs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075272%2Forg%2Faeb0ba791f12ecb43b0b19ecd682de37.jpg%2FeKi7Y4p3uz_36g6rLaM1zh6RNWq3NHf-hqtZy4arWcs&h=35e7ba3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3075169/org/b6a45442777534f18f7d9def19d335d4.jpg/C930RX-y--sCP3_naop4NUI-moq4pPVvbvSbW270m1s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075169%2Forg%2Fb6a45442777534f18f7d9def19d335d4.jpg%2FC930RX-y--sCP3_naop4NUI-moq4pPVvbvSbW270m1s&h=a3602001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3075273/org/a0d49241678e4cef6c30a34f9d249410.jpg/9bDLqHELOhP38Bsc3yLRWBX4lltyjiBLpzK_racyv60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3075273%2Forg%2Fa0d49241678e4cef6c30a34f9d249410.jpg%2F9bDLqHELOhP38Bsc3yLRWBX4lltyjiBLpzK_racyv60&h=0da08bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港產漫畫《古惑仔》曾被改編為人熟悉的《古惑仔》電影系列，90年代掀起一股黑幫電影的風潮。古惑仔在facebook發帖，貼出明日（25日）出版最新一期的漫畫封面，圖中可見一大群白衣人手執鐵通追打湧上樓梯的市民，令人不禁聯想周日（21日）元朗西鐵站內無差別襲擊事件。<br />\n<br />\n港產經典漫畫《古惑仔》於今日（24日）在facebook專頁公開明日發售2255期的漫畫封面，圖中一大群白衣人手持鐵通、雨傘等，追打一群戴頭盔、手無寸鐵的市民，令人聯想起周日（21日）晚上發生白衣人在元朗西鐵站無差別襲擊市民事件一幕。<br />\n<br />\n帖文一出後令一眾漫畫迷非常興奮，不少人揚言明天會買一本支持，「平時都冇睇開港產漫畫，今期點都要支持下」。漫畫主編文啟明（牛佬）前日發文表示，因近日「警民衝突」場面實為「百年難得一見」，故最近數期「值得一眾老友記擁有留念」。<br />\n<br />\n過往《古惑仔》曾以社會事件作題材，紀錄不少社會重要時刻，如雨傘革命、7月14日的新城市血戰一幕等，如在1765期的《古惑仔》封面，就繪畫了主角陳浩南撐黃傘、戴黃呔，如主角置身現實一樣。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：謝茜嘉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/355738/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB-%E5%8F%A4%E6%83%91%E4%BB%94-%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2-%E9%87%8D%E7%8F%BE%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%A5%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F355738%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%2583%2591%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%259D%25A2-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E5%2588%25A5%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%2595&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=cfab3ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/355738/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB-%E5%8F%A4%E6%83%91%E4%BB%94-%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2-%E9%87%8D%E7%8F%BE%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%A5%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%95</a>"},{"pid":"51ec51f61a434cc05119bafa457c73ae599387ba","tid":1370439,"uid":159266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"仲有大梵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255c42a70aca0e7a02afcddd0a1752a09223b9d5","tid":1370439,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6f1383b7553f85470e851ec87b15dc87e4cc23","tid":1370439,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:16:28.000Z","msg":"有時諗古惑仔係咪有外國勢力財政支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a32304d033db266981a8d0b15edf163d712a494","tid":1370439,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n大家今日出街一定要帶哨子，長遮！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqQbmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqQbmS</a>"},{"pid":"aae7bb087ce86b4c06c5556a6a76e42993204666","tid":1370439,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:32:10.000Z","msg":"啱先睇一睇啲大陸漫畫網<br />\n都睇到#1貼嗰堆封面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d318c8cb19c986c41dd637bf289d071d1dc10b70","tid":1370439,"uid":254386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"古惑仔而家可取既地方應該得返個封面，內容真係又拖又唔好睇"}]}